title: KTM 250 Duke vs Honda CBR250R vs Mahindra Mojo - The Financial Express
text: KTM 250 Duke vs Honda CBR250R vs Mahindra Mojo KTM 250 Duke vs Honda CBR250R vs Mahindra Mojo KTM India has finally launched the newest entrant in Duke family, the KTM 250 Duke, a quarter litre motorcycle, which is expected to give tough competition to the likes of Honda CBR250R and Mahindra Mojo. The 250 Duke is loaded with a host of features for the riders in safety, electronics and is priced competitively as well. In this comparo, we pit these motorcycles to find out , which one offers the best value-for-money in terms of performance and features.
